#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/textures/introduction.rst:40
msgid ""
"Your base *material*, which colors the whole surface in a uniform color that "
"reacts to light, giving different shades of the diffuse, specular, and "
"mirror colors based on the way light passes through and into the surface of "
"the object."
msgstr ""
"Votre *matériau* de base, qui colore la surface en u ne couleur uniforme qui "
"réagit à la lumière, en donnant différentes ombres de couleurs diffuses, "
